 Or for that matter, why were they not talking

56:35.260 --> 56:39.420
 about the killings in Donbass and Lugansk

56:39.420 --> 56:44.420
 during that 2014 to 2022 period?

56:45.300 --> 56:47.180
 That is what, it's a crime.

56:47.180 --> 56:49.540
 There were so many people that were killed,

