 It's a very good question.

57:13.380 --> 57:16.540
 What's the mistakes, what the human mistakes

57:16.540 --> 57:18.340
 and the leadership mistakes made by Vladimir Putin?

57:18.340 --> 57:19.180
 It's a very good question.

